title: Раскрыта стоимость роскошного наряда Артемия Лебедева
cleaned_sentences: Stylists of the sauce platform (previously - What's on the Star Russia) revealed the cost of a luxurious outfit of a blogger and designer Artemy Lebedev.
The corresponding post appeared in the Telegram channel of the project.
Fashion experts appreciated the image of a star consisting of a red elongated znwr down jacket for 48 thousand rubles and R13 jeans for 86.4 thousand rubles.
In addition, Lebedev appeared in the photo in the white shirt Jil Sander, the cost of which is 120 thousand rubles.
In addition, Influuanser put on MOMA sneakers for 43.9 thousand rubles, completing the appearance of Prada with leather gloves for 92 thousand rubles.
It is noted that the price of all products amounted to 390.3 thousand rubles.
In April, the cost of the luxurious image of Dmitry Nagiyev was disclosed.
The attention of fashion experts was attracted by the outfit of the 58-year-old artist for shooting in the journal "Dog.ru".
